%\epsfig{file=tempofracog100.ps,angle=90,width=0.9\linewidth,clip=}
\caption{\label{tempofracog100}
 The proton mean proper lifetime $\tau$ 
is plotted as a function of its proper acceleration $a$,
where we have assumed $\gamma = 100$. 
The result is not a very sensitive function of $\gamma$ 
provided that $\gamma \gg 1$. $\tau \propto 1/a^5$ 
for sufficiently large $a$.}
